description: The ASUS ZenBook 14 is an ultrathin ultrabook. It features an Intel Core i7 processor and 16GB of LPDDR4x RAM for seamless performance. The 14-inch Full HD NanoEdge display provides a stunning visual experience. With a 512GB SSD, it ensures speedy storage access.

The ASUS VivoBook S14 is a stylish and efficient everyday laptop. It's powered by an Intel Core i7 processor and boasts 16GB of LPDDR4x RAM for smooth multitasking. The 14-inch Full HD display offers clear visuals. With a fast 512GB SSD, it ensures quick boot times and application loading. This laptop is perfect for work and entertainment.

The ASUS VivoBook 15 is an ideal everyday laptop. It features an Intel Core i5 CPU and 12GB of DDR4 RAM for your daily computing needs. The 15.6-inch Full HD display offers clear visuals. With dual storage options (256GB SSD + 1TB HDD), it provides ample space for your files and apps.
